item.title: CVE-2022-43432|2024-08-03T13:32:59.234Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20xframium%20builder%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins XFramium Builder Plugin 1.0.22 and earlier programmatically disables Content-Security-Policy protection for user-generated content in workspaces, archived artifacts, etc. that Jenkins offers for download.
